snippet.textDisplay: I heard this song in 2012, I was in 4 standard, I loved it but couldn't understand the emotions involved and the depth of words. Now after so many years, I found it again and now I can actually feel the pain in this piece of art. The pain of separation and longing is so beautifully depicted in this masterpiece, it is enough to make you cry, even if you haven't gone through that pain.
